  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nAs mentioned [here](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/19350#issuecomment-1119351124), the quarkus-avro-extension currently does not support/process Avro [IDL](https://avro.apache.org/docs/current/idl.html#preamble) files like `sample.avdl`.\r\n\r\nSince the IDL is much easier to write compared to JSON, it would be good to have the extension pickup avdl files as well and generate the classes from there.\r\nCurrently we have to fall back to the avro-maven-plugin in order to do so.\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\n_No response_",
